<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 20:07:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与哈马斯重启谈判，公布人质交易“原则清单”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publishes-list-of-principles-for-hostage-deal-as-talks-with-hamas-renew/00000190-8eb4-d0cb-abb9-feb7f0a00000</link><description>外交消息人士对内塔尼亚胡的声明表示担忧，称总理“限制了自己和谈判团队”，但另一位消息人士指出“谈判中出现了真正的安全担忧”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 19:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publishes-list-of-principles-for-hostage-deal-as-talks-with-hamas-renew/00000190-8eb4-d0cb-abb9-feb7f0a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府出人意料地宣布建立以色列第一家阿拉伯文化博物馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/in-surprise-move-netanyahu-government-announces-israels-first-museum-of-arab-culture/00000190-8dd6-dcf1-afdd-ddf6a0e70000</link><description>以色列北部的 Umm al-Fahm 美术馆的目标之一是向游客介绍巴勒斯坦的叙事，该美术馆将在未来五年内获得 2200 万谢克尔（近 600 万美元），以达到国家博物馆标准</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:50:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/in-surprise-move-netanyahu-government-announces-israels-first-museum-of-arab-culture/00000190-8dd6-dcf1-afdd-ddf6a0e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的阿拉伯公民是否应该应征入伍——不是加入以色列国防军，而是服兵役？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/should-israels-arab-citizens-be-drafted-into-civilian-national-service/00000190-8d98-d591-a7ff-fffaf0780000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡联盟努力解决极端正统犹太人的兵役问题时，另一个主要社区免受以色列国防军征兵的约束：阿拉伯公民。尽管阿拉伯领导人对民用替代方案充满热情，但他们并不相信政府的意图。一位活动人士问道：“这个法西斯政府是否希望将我视为以色列成功故事的一部分？”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:46:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/should-israels-arab-citizens-be-drafted-into-civilian-national-service/00000190-8d98-d591-a7ff-fffaf0780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在加沙南部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-southern-gaza/00000190-8e29-d0cb-abb9-fe3bac970000</link><description>来自以色列北部德鲁兹村庄的 25 岁贾拉·易卜拉欣 (Jalaa Ibrahem) 少校周日在加沙地带被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/israeli-officer-killed-in-southern-gaza/00000190-8e29-d0cb-abb9-fe3bac970000</guid></item><item><title>英国新首相与以色列内塔尼亚胡通话，呼吁停火和人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/u-k-s-new-pm-speaks-with-israels-netanyahu-calls-for-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/00000190-8dca-d591-a7ff-fffa76c90000</link><description>总理基尔·斯塔默表示，他对以色列北部边境的局势感到“担忧” ■ 新当选的总理还与巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯进行了交谈</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/u-k-s-new-pm-speaks-with-israels-netanyahu-calls-for-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal/00000190-8dca-d591-a7ff-fffa76c90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列和内塔尼亚胡的看法已经过时，这是一个问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-07/ty-article/.highlight/biden-is-out-of-date-on-israel-and-netanyahu-and-its-a-problem/00000190-8dc0-d0cb-abb9-fff327b00000</link><description>作为一名经常撰写有关美以关系文章的以色列记者，有一件事是明确的：拜登对以色列政治的理解属于 20 世纪 80 年代，而不是当前时刻</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 17:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-07/ty-article/.highlight/biden-is-out-of-date-on-israel-and-netanyahu-and-its-a-problem/00000190-8dc0-d0cb-abb9-fff327b00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡与以色列国防部长就豁免极端正统派参军法案发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israels-defense-minister-clash-over-bill-exempting-ultra-orthodox-from-army/00000190-8ddd-de32-a79e-9fdd32cd0000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡等人与以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特就延长义务兵役期限和反对豁免极端正统派加入以色列国防军等问题展开激烈讨论</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 16:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israels-defense-minister-clash-over-bill-exempting-ultra-orthodox-from-army/00000190-8ddd-de32-a79e-9fdd32cd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 275 天：埃及将接待以色列和美国代表团进行停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-275-egypt-to-host-israeli-u-s-delegations-for-truce-talks/00000190-8df4-d0cb-abb9-fff7781e0001</link><description>据报道，埃及将接待以色列和美国代表团，讨论人质释放谈判中的“突出问题” ■ 消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列周末提出了新要求，预计将推迟达成可能的协议 ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了 50 多枚火箭弹 ■ 数千人参加以色列各地针对人质交易和提​​前选举举行为期一天的抗议活动 ■ 战争进入 275 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 16:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-275-egypt-to-host-israeli-u-s-delegations-for-truce-talks/00000190-8df4-d0cb-abb9-fff7781e0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列检方反对内塔尼亚胡推迟腐败审判证词的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-prosecution-objects-to-netanyahus-request-to-postpone-corruption-trial-testimony/00000190-8d58-d443-adbe-ad5ab6740000</link><description>检方希望审判不晚于 11 月继续进行。法官现在需要审查双方的请求，并定于周二就此事举行听证会</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 14:46:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-prosecution-objects-to-netanyahus-request-to-postpone-corruption-trial-testimony/00000190-8d58-d443-adbe-ad5ab6740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家劳工法庭裁定同性伴侣的男性可以被定义为家庭主妇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-national-labor-court-rules-man-in-same-sex-partnership-can-be-defined-as-homemaker/00000190-8d58-d5d5-a1b5-8d78600c0000</link><description>法院裁定，保险法中仅使用“家庭主妇”一词的男性和女性之间的语言区别是歧视性的，并且基于古老的世界观</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 13:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-national-labor-court-rules-man-in-same-sex-partnership-can-be-defined-as-homemaker/00000190-8d58-d5d5-a1b5-8d78600c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列缺乏战后加沙计划可能会加剧停火反对者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-an-israeli-plan-for-postwar-gaza-could-boost-cease-fire-opponents/00000190-8ce0-dd37-a5f7-bee2a2120000</link><description>如果没有其他选择，哈马斯官员可能会在停火达成后控制加沙 ■ 如果以色列不做出决定，建立军事政权将提上议程</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 12:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/lack-of-an-israeli-plan-for-postwar-gaza-could-boost-cease-fire-opponents/00000190-8ce0-dd37-a5f7-bee2a2120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府，呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-protesters-rally-across-israel-to-demand-gaza-hostage-deal-early-elections/00000190-8c97-dbb7-afbf-cd9f2d930000</link><description>在“抵抗日”，示威者封锁了十字路口，并聚集在部长官邸和该国劳工联合会总部外</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 10:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-protesters-rally-across-israel-to-demand-gaza-hostage-deal-early-elections/00000190-8c97-dbb7-afbf-cd9f2d930000</guid></item><item><title>“奇迹时代”：以色列极右翼部长对约旦河西岸定居点扩建感到高兴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/era-of-miracles-israeli-far-right-minister-rejoices-at-west-bank-settlement-expansion/00000190-8bf3-dbb7-afbf-cffb409f0000</link><description>国家宣教部长奥里特·斯特罗克 (Orit Strock) 参观了希伯伦附近即将合法化的一个前哨基地，并表示在那里定居是她的首要任务</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 07:15:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/era-of-miracles-israeli-far-right-minister-rejoices-at-west-bank-settlement-expansion/00000190-8bf3-dbb7-afbf-cffb409f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军于 10 月 7 日下令汉尼拔指令，防止哈马斯俘虏士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-ordered-hannibal-directive-on-october-7-to-prevent-hamas-taking-soldiers-captive/00000190-89a2-d776-a3b1-fdbe45520000</link><description>“人们陷入了疯狂的歇斯底里，在没有经过核实的信息的情况下就开始做出决定”：《国土报》获得的文件和证词显示，汉尼拔的行动命令，指示使用武力防止士兵被俘虏，是在被渗透的三个军队设施中使用的。哈马斯也可能危及平民</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 03:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-ordered-hannibal-directive-on-october-7-to-prevent-hamas-taking-soldiers-captive/00000190-89a2-d776-a3b1-fdbe45520000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯人质谈判进入关键阶段，外国领导人对内塔尼亚胡混杂的信息感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/with-hostage-talks-in-crucial-phase-foreign-leaders-are-perplexed-by-pms-mixed-messages/00000190-89af-dd37-a5f7-bbef61630000</link><description>过去几天，国际社会一直试图弄清内塔尼亚胡的意图。他是否希望达成一项能够实现更广泛停火的协议，或者这些举措是为了在协议最终遭到破坏之前安抚公众舆论并缓解国际压力？</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 02:38:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/with-hostage-talks-in-crucial-phase-foreign-leaders-are-perplexed-by-pms-mixed-messages/00000190-89af-dd37-a5f7-bbef61630000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人和美国公民在真主党火箭弹和导弹袭击中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-live/cia-chief-to-meet-with-israel-egypt-and-qatar-ahead-of-renewed-hostage-deal-talks/00000190-8ae4-d41a-a3dc-9ef4d5080000</link><description>整个周日，大约有 50 枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射 ■ 周日的示威活动要求在“抵抗日”达成反政府人质协议，距 10 月 7 日已有 9 个月了 ■ 美国公民重伤、以色列中度受伤、士兵和士兵真主党从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射火箭弹，以色列平民受轻伤 ■ 哈马斯在人质协议第一阶段放弃持久停火的要求并接受协议；内塔尼亚胡表示“差距仍然存在”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 01:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-live/cia-chief-to-meet-with-israel-egypt-and-qatar-ahead-of-renewed-hostage-deal-talks/00000190-8ae4-d41a-a3dc-9ef4d5080000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列的新要求预计将推迟人质交易的完成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-demands-are-expected-to-delay-completion-of-hostage-deal-sources-say/00000190-89b1-d8b2-a3b6-fdff13d80000</link><description>摩萨德负责人大卫·巴尼亚向调解员提供了以色列新的保留清单，其中一些是关于在当地实施停火的措辞。据以色列消息人士称，谈判预计至少持续三周才能达成协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 00:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-demands-are-expected-to-delay-completion-of-hostage-deal-sources-say/00000190-89b1-d8b2-a3b6-fdff13d80000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日涉嫌杀害一名巴勒斯坦人的三名以色列人中至少有一人不太可能受到指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/some-of-the-israelis-suspected-of-murdering-palestinian-on-oct-7-unlikely-to-be-charged/00000190-8970-d41a-a3dc-9d70f1e70000</link><description>这三名嫌疑人不属于以色列安全部队，涉嫌射杀当天早上从加沙进入以色列的一名手无寸铁的巴勒斯坦人。调查消息传出后，MK Gantz 表示，所有 10 月 7 日进入以色列的加沙人“都将被判处死刑”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 00:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/some-of-the-israelis-suspected-of-murdering-palestinian-on-oct-7-unlikely-to-be-charged/00000190-8970-d41a-a3dc-9d70f1e70000</guid></item><item><title>1967 年西墙标志性照片中的伞兵去世，享年 81 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/paratrooper-in-iconic-1967-western-wall-photograph-dies-at-81/00000190-8950-d0d9-a1f9-aff6187a0000</link><description>伊扎克·伊法特（Yitzhak Yifat）被拍成了以色列历史上最著名的照片之一，几天后他告诉《国土报》，虽然他不信教，但在那些时刻他“感受到了一些东西”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 19:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/paratrooper-in-iconic-1967-western-wall-photograph-dies-at-81/00000190-8950-d0d9-a1f9-aff6187a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在深入黎巴嫩境内的袭击中杀死了真主党特工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-hezbollah-operative-in-drone-strike-deep-inside-lebanese-territory/00000190-8956-dc2c-a9fa-ed5eb93b0000</link><description>据以色列军方称，这名真主党特工是该组织防空系统的关键专家，参与了针对以色列的各种行动的规划和执行</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 18:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-hezbollah-operative-in-drone-strike-deep-inside-lebanese-territory/00000190-8956-dc2c-a9fa-ed5eb93b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>